--- Fortigate Shell Help ---

help: this help.

show network [network_name]: without parameter, displays all the checkpoint
  network objects. Or displays the network object 'network_name'.

show policy-routes: displays the policy route rules set

show rules: displays the firewall rules set.

show service [service_name]: without parameter, displays all the checkpoint
  services. Or displays the service 'service_name'.

show snat-rules: displays the central SNAT rules set

xref ip     :see help xref-ip.
xref service: see help xref-service.xref ip : see help xref.

